cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper discusses the recent literature on automatic keyword extraction and text summarization, which are important areas in natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses different methodologies used for keyword extraction and text summarization, which involves information retrieval techniques, machine learning algorithms, and deep learning models. Hence, it can also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
